  "detailed_description": "Become an elite pilot of special Robot Squad.<br />\r\nUse specialized, remotely controlled robots, which you will control yourself.<br />\r\nDeal with the hardest missions which can't be performed directly by people due to the conditions.<br />\r\nHuman life and safety is in your hands!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGame features:<br />\r\n- 4 different robots: 2 terrestrial, aerial and underwater<br />\r\n- 6 training missions<br />\r\n- 16 story missions which take place all over the world, in different settings<br />\r\n- 10 different accessories mounted on robots<br />\r\n- plenty of gameplay elements like: guards, explosives, mechanisms<br />\r\n- upgrading parameters of robots and accessories<br />\r\n- different types of missions: rescue, spy, exploration, military",
  "about_the_game": "Become an elite pilot of special Robot Squad.<br />\r\nUse specialized, remotely controlled robots, which you will control yourself.<br />\r\nDeal with the hardest missions which can't be performed directly by people due to the conditions.<br />\r\nHuman life and safety is in your hands!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGame features:<br />\r\n- 4 different robots: 2 terrestrial, aerial and underwater<br />\r\n- 6 training missions<br />\r\n- 16 story missions which take place all over the world, in different settings<br />\r\n- 10 different accessories mounted on robots<br />\r\n- plenty of gameplay elements like: guards, explosives, mechanisms<br />\r\n- upgrading parameters of robots and accessories<br />\r\n- different types of missions: rescue, spy, exploration, military",
